Packaged by Neha Sharma <neha@fnal.gov>

The upstream source tarball for Bestman is created by the following procedure:

- cd in to [working_dir]
- svn checkout https://codeforge.lbl.gov/anonscm/bestman
- mv bestman bestman2
- cd bestman2
- rm -rf tags 
- rm -rf bestman2/tags
- find . -name .svn -print0 | xargs -0 rm -rf
- cd ../
- tar -cvzf bestman2.tar.gz bestman2

The tarball that contains the dependencies can be downloaded from
http://vdt.cs.wisc.edu/upstream/bestman2/2.2.1a/dependent.jars.tar.gz
